{"commentv2": 1, "number": 6, "id": 270635, "nreplies": 9, "sticky": 0, "user": "144334", "body": "In case you guys didn't know, Nefarian and Onyxia are brother and sister.", "date": "2008-04-12T12:00:04-05:00", "rating": 144, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "And the Children of Deathwing", "creationdate": "2011-08-10T08:25:29-05:00", "id": 257747, "rating": 53, "commentid": 270635, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "sskain", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Sinestra is their mother, actually. Another brother is Sabellian in Blade's Edge Mountains.", "creationdate": "2012-06-03T13:18:58-05:00", "id": 547550, "rating": 24, "commentid": 270635, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 256, "username": "Reignac", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "And another brother Wrathion in Tavern in the Mists.", "creationdate": "2013-01-16T15:10:42-06:00", "id": 623348, "rating": 31, "commentid": 270635, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Giondi", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Why down vote Giondi? He is correct. Wrathion is Deathwings child aswell", "creationdate": "2013-09-04T09:55:49-05:00", "id": 689518, "rating": 8, "commentid": 270635, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Tyerr", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "He also refers to Deathwing as his father, Auntie is probably just a title he uses due to the fact Onyixa is a broodmother, and thus very old in mortal terms, where as Wrathion is but a mere whelp.", "creationdate": "2015-05-25T11:19:48-05:00", "id": 871554, "rating": 1, "commentid": 270635, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 256, "username": "Skullhawk13", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 7, "id": 284012, "nreplies": 2, "sticky": 0, "user": "93865", "body": "Upon entering Nefarian's room, he sits upon his throne in human form, flagged as friendly and unattackable. You may enter into dialogue with him, the end of which begins the encounter (similar to Ragnaros, Shade of Akama and the NPCs in Mount Hyjal). \r\n\r\nDialogue is as follows:\r\n\r\nNefarian: \"Do you expect me to cower before the mighty legion of <player>? You are nothing to me. Less than nothing. Had I desired your head, it would have been presented to me on a pike.\r\n\r\n\"You have made the mistake that all mortals make.\r\n\"*Victor Nefarius sighs.*\r\n\r\n\"Time does strange things to those that use it as a form of currency.\"\r\n\r\nPlayer: \"I\u2019ve made no mistakes. \"\r\n\r\nNefarian: \"In your rush to glory, you assumed that the pace of this game revolved around your actions. Can you even fathom how preposterous that sounds to a being like me? A being that if so inclined could cause your own insignificant thoughts to crush the peanut sized mass of grey matter floating within your skull?\"\r\n\r\nPlayer: \"You have lost your mind. You speak in riddles.\"\r\n\r\nNefarian: \"It's simple really! Allow me to summarize\u2026\"\r\n\r\nPlayer: \"Please do. \"\r\n\r\nNefarian: \"In this world where time is your enemy, it is my greatest ally. This grand game of life that you think you play in fact plays you. To that I say\u2026 \"\r\n\r\n(at this point dialogue ends and Nefarian becomes hostile; the final line is a verbal emote)\r\nNefarian: \"Let the games begin!\"", "date": "2008-05-07T12:49:53-05:00", "rating": 97, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "In Soviet Blackrock, game of life plays you!", "creationdate": "2012-06-02T20:39:02-05:00", "id": 547407, "rating": 22, "commentid": 284012, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "pynkskyn", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "*runs for the cornucopia* *Ignores Haymitch's advice*", "creationdate": "2012-06-11T17:21:00-05:00", "id": 549256, "rating": 12, "commentid": 284012, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Frpw", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2008-05-07T12:50:17-05:00", 1, "93865"]}
