{"commentv2": 1, "number": 9, "id": 343736, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "43910", "body": "Doing this fight at level 70:\n\n-Your main tank MUST have the Onyxia Scale Cloak equipped, since does a perodic cone-shaped shadow flame.\n\n-When phase 2 starts and he is about to land, anyone who is NOT wearing an Onyxia Scale Cloak will receive ~50k damage and die unless they prevent it in some way - meaning Divine Shield, Iceblock, Shield Wall, Cloak of Shadows etc. LOS abuse doesn't seem to prevent this from hitting you, altough we had a few people magically not dying from it.\n\nCombat ress if any druids managed to survive, and bring him down to 20%. (Might take a while.)\nThe huge amount of Bone Constructs are easily dealt with, have a protection paladin pick them up or cast Blessing of Protection on a warlock/mage and have them do it.\n\nWe did this with one player (the tank) actually having the cloak, and about 15 survivors of the Shadow Flame.", "date": "2008-08-03T18:17:11-05:00", "rating": 8, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2008-08-03T18:19:33-05:00", 1, "43910"]}
