{"commentv2": 1, "number": 13, "id": 543638, "nreplies": 5, "sticky": 0, "user": "LadyAyne", "body": "*  Death Knights:\r\n          - Quote: \"Death Knights, get over here!\"\r\n          - Effect: Casts Death Grip on the entire raid, pulling everyone inside his hitbox.\r\n          - Solution: Simply run back to your positions - unlike the Rogue call, this one does not immobilize teleported players for the duration.", "date": "2009-01-02T20:33:42-06:00", "rating": 50, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Probably a parody on Scorpion from Mortal Kombat (\"Get over here!\")", "creationdate": "2009-01-18T12:16:02-06:00", "id": 381486, "rating": 21, "commentid": 543638, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 256, "username": "Vlad", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Ya think...", "creationdate": "2009-04-05T20:21:00-05:00", "id": 398043, "rating": 13, "commentid": 543638, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Ragus", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Confirmed. Death Grips raid into him.", "creationdate": "2009-07-26T17:42:59-05:00", "id": 417365, "rating": 3, "commentid": 543638, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "421626", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "never really seed DK's calling  he pulls you in front of his cleaving arms or what?  because DK's fight at close range normally, so it move sou only from sides to head?", "creationdate": "2011-07-03T15:51:30-05:00", "id": 487561, "rating": 2, "commentid": 543638, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Daralyn", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}