{"commentv2": 1, "number": 14, "id": 568319, "nreplies": 4, "sticky": 0, "user": "Vlad", "body": "Now that Cataclysm is out the fight has changed, a lot. You no longer need the [item=15138] at all -so you don't have to hide behind the throne any longer. The debuff will not kill you on the last tick, hurray for that! [i]I kept the old post for historical purposes, in spoiler tags.[/i]\n\n[spoiler]If you do not have the [item=15138] you can manage this event with a minimum of 1 tank and 2 healers (+some dps, the more the faster/easier for healers). The shadow flame ticks around 1k dmg -no problem what so ever but at the end at the debuff it deals [b]16k damage[/b]! This means the tank needs to be on full health (at least over 16k hp) before debuff runs out! (And the only one standing in-front getting the shadowflames) Just have the tank capped off and its easy to survive. The more dps you bring along, the less healing you have to do as well!\n\n[b]To survive the transaction phase 1 -> phase 2, simply have everyone behind the throne.[/b] When you see Nefarious yell, wait 10 sec and rush out to pick him up, face him away from the raid asap! The last phase when all mobs you killed in phase 1 spawn is easy to kill, they hit for nothing really. Did this with 10 people, no problems at all (only had 1 warlock as AoE class -didn't see him AoE either :P). Worst call is hunters, no one has a macro or addon to remove ranged item in this fight, ends up getting their damage reduced to almost nothing...\n\nUnfortunately no addons are kept update from the old era so they do not work with WotLK client. Thus you must manage the old way where you read emotes in the chat frame. [i][small]It's a fun fight, nothing hard compared to doing Razorgore 6 man (haha), doable too but hard. 2nd boss is also a bit tricky as you die from the debuff he casts (bomb), simply nuke and use Soulstone and Ankhs if you have shamans and warlocks![/small][/i][/spoiler]", "date": "2009-01-18T17:23:43-06:00", "rating": 30, "indent": 0, "roles": 256, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Adding a macro for hunters. Use this when the 5 second call warning appears (if you have a addon for it ofc) -use macro to save ranged item. Use macro again to equip the item. Keep first slot in backpack free during the fight (used for the ranged weapon)!  [code]/run local s=\"RangedSlot\";local d=GetInventorySlotInfo(s);if GetInventoryItemLink(\"player\",d)then PickupInventoryItem(d)PutItemInBackpack()else PickupContainerItem(0,1)EquipCursorItem(d)end[/code]", "creationdate": "2009-02-07T17:51:38-06:00", "id": 78596, "rating": 20, "commentid": 568319, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 256, "username": "Vlad", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "There's an easier macro: /unequip slot 18 [weapon] /equip slot 18 [weapon]  I used a similar macro with slots 16 and 17 for my warrior when i did pvp, mostly for spell reflect or revenge spam.", "creationdate": "2009-10-05T00:25:26-05:00", "id": 125909, "rating": 9, "commentid": 568319, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Tyuru", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "This doesn't appear to work anymore, unfortunately.", "creationdate": "2010-12-26T17:41:09-06:00", "id": 208476, "rating": 5, "commentid": 568319, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 256, "username": "Mondoblasto", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "just keep some other bow/gun with you, then have a macro like this /unequip (insert name of wep you are using) /equip (other wep you brought) then have another macro (can probably make it all into one macro but im not sure) /unequip (the other wep you brought) /equip (good wep) boom, or just have the heirloom bow since it has no durability therefore can't brake, or just manually switch weps, various ways to handle this", "creationdate": "2013-07-10T11:34:43-05:00", "id": 676345, "rating": 0, "commentid": 568319, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Zaron31116", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2011-10-02T07:18:35-05:00", 2, "Vlad"]}
