{"commentv2": 1, "number": 16, "id": 638774, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "178348", "body": "I ran BWL with ~25 people last week on my retribution paladin.  I was the only one wearing an Onyxia Scale Cloak.  Most everyone died within the first 30 seconds except an 80 or two.  They died within a minute after everyone else died.  I was able to solo him until ~300k health, but then he summoned all of his skeletons.  I used holy wrath, consecrate, and bubbled right before I died.  I was able to full heal before the bubble wore off.  I died soon after, but all of the skeletons were at ~5-10% health.  My lay on hands was on cooldown, otherwise I might have been able to finish him off.", "date": "2009-03-11T09:53:14-05:00", "rating": -2, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
