{"commentv2": 1, "number": 19, "id": 794904, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "cryptoengineer", "body": "My guild ran BWL for the achievement last night. About a dozen, mostly 80s with a couple low-mid 70s. Only half of us had cloaks. None of the earlier bosses were serious challenges. \r\n\r\nThis boss was different. The dragonkin were no problem, but once the boss showed up, all the non-cloaked died very quickly, even those who claimed they were hiding behind the throne. We were left with 2 priests, a holy pally, 2 DKs and a warrior, all with cloaks. We were able, without too much trouble, to slowly 6-man him down, and AOE the adds at 20%. After that, it was cake.\r\n\r\nThe cloaks (which we bought on the AH) were clearly the deciding factor.", "date": "2009-08-01T09:38:17-05:00", "rating": 1, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
