{"commentv2": 1, "number": 25, "id": 851678, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "Tairne", "body": "I'd like to confirm that Nefarian now drops 1 or maybe 2 Tier 2 head pieces after the Onyxia revamp.\r\nI ran it just a minute ago and Nemesis Skullcap dropped, the one that recieved that item also got an achievement: [Onyxia's Lair (60)].\r\nIf this is a bug is still unsure, but we can all be happy for one thing, the tier 2 item set is not completely lost!", "date": "2009-09-25T15:11:22-05:00", "rating": 11, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Probably what happened is that currently the helms are tagged as \"Criteria of: Onyxia's Lair\". That's my best guess, probably won't be long before it's fixed", "creationdate": "2009-09-27T20:10:22-05:00", "id": 124698, "rating": 4, "commentid": 851678, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "360080", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
