{"commentv2": 1, "number": 41, "id": 1285964, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "755080", "body": "Nefarian is a fun but challenging fight when you raid with all 60's, he does have a few bugs that makes him a much harder boss which is good can't always have easy raid bosses like now a days, well the bugs are in the beginning of the fight, the drakonids spawn quickly so it is an issue for our warrior tanks to grab all of the mobs and when they get ressurected it causes major lag and even disconnection problems, and hopefully blizzard gets the chance to fix this problem if they don't its no problem it is still a do able fight.", "date": "2011-01-09T14:21:02-06:00", "rating": -5, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
