{"commentv2": 1, "number": 43, "id": 1345406, "nreplies": 4, "sticky": 0, "user": "784022", "body": "I just attempted to kill this guy today, about at 11:30pm, when we got him to 80% he just simply despawned and never showed back up, or respawned, anyone have any idea why?", "date": "2011-02-21T22:48:47-06:00", "rating": 8, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "He has a 10-15 minute respawn timer apparently. Just wait it out, and he will respawn sitting on the throne.", "creationdate": "2011-02-22T17:57:25-06:00", "id": 227497, "rating": 9, "commentid": 1345406, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "206036", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Thanks.. I was quite sure I waited that long, but I could be wrong, time passes at a snail's pace when your not doing anything ^^:", "creationdate": "2011-02-27T02:16:37-06:00", "id": 228644, "rating": 2, "commentid": 1345406, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "784022", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "One reason he will despawn is, if you're a hunter soling the encounter and FD, the encounter will reset. Learned this the hard way... MD to pet to lose aggro instead. ;-)", "creationdate": "2013-01-06T21:05:18-06:00", "id": 619992, "rating": 0, "commentid": 1345406, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Bethgael", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "asked a GM about the respawn time, they responded with 20 minutes.", "creationdate": "2014-06-16T07:25:10-05:00", "id": 751625, "rating": 0, "commentid": 1345406, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Refticus", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, 