{"commentv2": 1, "number": 48, "id": 1494890, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "Rederoin", "body": "I solo'd this as a MM hunter, for those wanting to do the same :\r\n\r\nSpam misdirect in phase 1 & 3. Never use a multi shot without misdirect.(unless you're sure your not getting aggro).  Getting aggro is not the end of the world, it does however take you more time to solo him.    Also,  don't use FD. Its bugged for some reason(Nefarian despawns if you use it in Phase 1.)", "date": "2011-08-14T12:51:36-05:00", "rating": 4, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 49, "id": 1501575, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "870378", "body": "Soloed as frost dps DK with pvp gear, never went below 80% hp... he is really easy... on the other side CHromagus was hard, but managed as blood with dps gear and that Venom sac to cleanse green debuff.", "date": "2011-08-23T07:44:37-05:00", "rating": -1, "indent": 0, "roles": 16384, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 50, "id": 1507910, "nreplies": 3, "sticky": 0, "user": "Vinland", "body": "Just faced him on my Hunter having soloed the whole place, used FD to drop aggro after he went into dragon form and he despawned completely. Didn't come back either. Massive waste of time.", "date": "2011-09-01T04:47:14-05:00", "rating": 11, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "As far as the didn't respond thing goes - in Vanilla, he had a 15 minute respawn timer. I'm sure that is still the case today unless they changed something over the years that I missed.", "creationdate": "2011-09-01T21:08:58-05:00", "id": 262022, "rating": 9, "commentid": 1507910, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Sonata", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "He does still indeed have an 15 min respawn time, if you fail on him, or if he bugs somehow.", "creationdate": "2011-10-30T17:08:00-05:00", "id": 274285, "rating": 11, "commentid": 1507910, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Eukanubae", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Just happened to me(bugged), im gonna wait and check if he respawns...", "creationdate": "2013-11-17T20:11:20-06:00", "id": 708833, "rating": 0, "commentid": 1507910, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Krakatua", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
