{"commentv2": 1, "number": 53, "id": 1664157, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "Hazuki11", "body": "Is it just me, or is there something unlucky about druids? Now I understand I never shall have restoration/Balance/bear tank druids with me in there, every 25-35 sec they'll be turned into a cat form for 30 sec, which means they wont have more than almost only 1-5 sec to cast a healing or damaging spell before they are turned into cat form again... Stupid!", "date": "2012-05-08T05:53:50-05:00", "rating": -7, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "Keep in mind that Nefarian only calls out a single class at a time. The more class diversity in your raid, the less likely a particular one class will be called out.", "creationdate": "2012-07-15T03:11:03-05:00", "id": 556946, "rating": 2, "commentid": 1664157, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "KeleturShask", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 54, "id": 1688279, "nreplies": 3, "sticky": 0, "user": "KeleturShask", "body": "Does anyone have any word on if Nefarian calls out Monks?", "date": "2012-07-15T03:22:18-05:00", "rating": 61, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "I don't know, but I'm gonna laugh so hard if he makes them stumble around in a drunken stupor with a massive loss of hit chance.", "creationdate": "2012-09-16T09:36:23-05:00", "id": 571803, "rating": 33, "commentid": 1688279, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Calydor", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "That's actually a really good idea, Calydor.", "creationdate": "2012-10-01T01:46:34-05:00", "id": 576952, "rating": 12, "commentid": 1688279, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "KeleturShask", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Just did this on my monk, and he does indeed have a monk class call :) He yells \"Monks, doesn't all that rolling make you dizzy?\" and I uncontrollably went rolling forward for about 5 secs", "creationdate": "2012-11-11T15:39:25-06:00", "id": 598030, "rating": 47, "commentid": 1688279, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Adalena", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 55, "id": 1777031, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "schnookems", "body": "I just wanted to confirm [url=#comments:id=1507910]Vinland's comment replies[/url] about his respawn timer, after patch 5.1. I ended up with all of Chromaggus' debuffs and was forced into cat form so I could not heal/survive through the fight.\n\nAfter waiting 10-15minutes, Nefarian respawned on his throne to begin the encounter again from the start.", "date": "2012-12-07T04:42:52-06:00", "rating": 18, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "\"In this world where time is your enemy, it is my greatest ally.\"", "creationdate": "2013-01-24T01:32:23-06:00", "id": 625852, "rating": 5, "commentid": 1777031, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "yzerman", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2012-12-07T04:43:07-06:00", 1, "schnookems"]}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 56, "id": 1784261, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "Snorbuckle", "body": "Nefarian now has a Monk class call. He yells \"Monks, doesn't all that rolling make you dizzy?\" and forces players into a roll for a number of seconds.", "date": "2012-12-19T18:17:32-06:00", "rating": 117, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "5 seconds to be exact!", "creationdate": "2014-10-09T06:33:10-05:00", "id": 777514, "rating": 9, "commentid": 1784261, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Savil", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
