{"commentv2": 1, "number": 59, "id": 1846231, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "Morbius", "body": "Soloed this with my 85 DK in blood spec wearing Jade Forest greens and auction house blues. My equipped item level is 417.\n\n I had never done this fight before so when I got swarmed with all the drakonids I didn't know what was going on. I finally figured out that you have to fight them until Nefarian transforms into a dragon and lands on the balcony. After that I ignored the adds and let my DOTs kill them after spreading them with Boil Blood with Roiling Blood talent. The death knight call is kind of silly, all he does is death grip you which forces him to back up.\n\nHere's the video:\nhttp://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VtifU4PAHkc", "date": "2013-04-23T12:43:52-05:00", "rating": 2, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2013-04-23T13:20:02-05:00", 3, "Morbius"]}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 60, "id": 1860181, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "Catweazle", "body": "I don't know if this is a bug or intended but ever since 5.3 the skeletons that come out during the end portion of the fight now spawn in ridiculously massive numbers. There must have been hundreds of them, my game was lagging and they actually almost killed me at level 90. Probably not an issue for classes with good AOE abilities but for others it could be an issue. There was a massive pile of them when I finally did get them killed.", "date": "2013-05-30T15:45:41-05:00", "rating": 11, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 61, "id": 1874309, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "alvraen", "body": "Monks now roll continuously forward.", "date": "2013-07-06T20:12:51-05:00", "rating": -5, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 62, "id": 1881325, "nreplies": 1, "sticky": 0, "user": "Aenonar", "body": "Be [b]very[/b] careful when doing this boss other than solo. In the first stage Nefarian loves to silence casters and the summoned mobs loves to mind control one of you unless you tag them asap in melee range!\r\n\r\nI've dualboxed him several times by now but last run with my warrior + druid I planned to let the druid do all the AoE. But I happened to be silenced at the start and had a 1-2 second overlap on the first mobs at which the warrior got mindcontrolled and instakilled the druid. Fight reset and I had to wait 15 minutes for Nefarian to return.\r\n\r\nSecond try i happened to leave 1 second gap between the thunderstorms and the same thing happened, warrior got MC'd and instakilled the druid. Another 15 minutes to reset..\r\n\r\nThird try I made sure the warrior was also in combat but the druid got silenced and then mind controlled and 2 shot the warrior instead! Easy res but another 15 minutes to reset...\r\n\r\nFourth try I made sure the druid was constantly casting thunderstorm and warrior casually hitting stuff, success...\r\n\r\n\r\nNever happened that extreme before, sometimes one was MC'd but the never instakilled the other... But it could easily happen, especially with the silence from Nefairan.\r\n\r\n\r\nSo make sure everyone are actively fighting as that seem to avoid the mind control! If you do get silenced, at least hit something with melee etc.", "date": "2013-07-27T11:08:04-05:00", "rating": 12, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "once me and my guildies were doing it and our balance druid got mc'd, one shotted both of us with starfire that did 200k overkill to me and set new record for biggest hit taken", "creationdate": "2014-10-12T23:52:48-05:00", "id": 778211, "rating": 2, "commentid": 1881325, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "jxli", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
