{"commentv2": 1, "number": 4, "id": 1202423, "nreplies": 4, "sticky": 0, "user": "OverlordAxefury", "body": "technically he is a undead dragon like his sister at you see his gut is spit open in 3d module viewer and his skin is called DragonNefarianZombified1", "date": "2010-12-02T15:11:24-06:00", "rating": 72, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [{"body": "This is also evident in the 3D model viewer, as his scales are dark grey, green, and purple, rather than their majestic onyx, red, and orange. Furthermore, his throat has been garroted, and his intestines are spilling out. His ribs are exposed, and his belly is as well. His wings are also incredibly tattered, and torn. This is very obviously a reanimated Nefarian.", "creationdate": "2010-12-21T22:12:55-06:00", "id": 206789, "rating": 46, "commentid": 1202423, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "Wenduri", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "have u also noticed he still has his head? no matter how many ppl turned it in for the city wide yelling by the leader he still has his head along with poor Ony. oh well.", "creationdate": "2010-12-23T15:23:42-06:00", "id": 207446, "rating": 80, "commentid": 1202423, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "552445", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "That's why  his head dissapears after a while from the orgrimmar pike.", "creationdate": "2011-01-06T20:10:43-06:00", "id": 212598, "rating": 78, "commentid": 1202423, "dataTree": 1, "roles": 0, "username": "stathisdjs", "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "downvotedByUser": false, "reportedByUser": false, "votedByUser": false}, {"body": "Why do you think deathwing attacked stormwind and orgrimar? The rp going out to vashjir touches on it a little