{"commentv2": 1, "number": 74, "id": 2505395, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "Namue", "body": "Ok, it's patch 7.2.5 now (iirc) and I'm trying to run this on my 105 mage with ilvl 727. I've been running a lot of old raids for transmog and achievements so I have it set to heroic and so far have had no problems. \r\n\r\nThis fight? Seems impossible. I try and spam as many hits on Nef when he is circling but I can never get him lower than 50% before he runs behind his sister, who promptly destroys me. \r\n\r\nI tried to kill Ony first but I got squished anyway\r\n\r\nWent back to trying to just trying to kill Nef as fast as possible, then jumped down to finish him off because the jerk gets out of range when he descends. By the time I get into the pit I'm already dead from the hits.\r\n\r\nDoes the damage done scale to level or something? How could I be able to breeze through all the other content, and then this fight knocks me out in a minute flat.  Or am I missing some mechanic?\r\n\r\n=/ I'm not real happy about this kind of thing. I want to run legacy dungeons and raids and have fun, not get killed when I'm supposed to be op. \r\n\r\nI finally switched to normal just to finish the raid, and was able to kill Nef right as he landed, but I was still taking rediculous amounts of damage and ended the fight with about a third of my health left. \r\n\r\n?", "date": "2017-07-01T21:32:44-05:00", "rating": 2, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
{"commentv2": 1, "number": 75, "id": 2557962, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "Teot", "body": "If you are a ranged class, or have some ranged damage ability, after you activate the orb just stay there until he flies by.  As a hunter I was able to shoot him from where the orb is and then jump down and loot him.  This was so less painful than running around to try and get close to him while on the floor.", "date": "2018-03-14T23:43:20-05:00", "rating": 8, "indent": 0, "roles": 0, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
