{"commentv2": 1, "number": 0, "id": 3148744, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "Nynaeve", "body": "[npc=151779] is taught via [item=172016], which is set to be obtained during the [url=https://ptr.wowhead.com/event=808/wows-15th-anniversary]15th Anniversary event[/url].\r\n\r\nWhile most of his abilities seem to be shared with several other battle pets, he does seem to have one unique one, as well as a very rare one.\r\nWhile unique doesn't necessarily mean useful, these two abilities do seem fairly interesting, assuming you have an all-dragon(kin) battle pet team. \r\n\r\n[pet-ability=2283] is an ability seemingly all his own.\r\n[pet-ability=1956] seems to be shared with just one other battle pet, [npc=127852].", "date": "2019-08-20T16:43:51-05:00", "rating": 2, "indent": 0, "roles": 256, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}}
