{"commentv2": 1, "number": 2, "id": 3169358, "nreplies": 0, "sticky": 0, "user": "Sipder2", "body": "[item=172016] is reward from [item=172014]. \nAs soon as the event goes live, you can log in and will receive the achievement [achievement=13917], and an [item=172014] in your mail. In your gift you will receive:\n\n[ul]\n[li][item=172016] - Gives the [npc=151779] battle pet.[/li]\n[li][item=172015] - Increases experience and reputation gains by 15%. This lasts until the event ends.[/li]\n[li][item=172013] - A reusable firework that can be used for the duration of the event.[/li]\n[li][item=172018] and [item=172019] - Chests of balloons.[/li]\n[li][item=172017] - An item to pop the above balloons.[/li]\n[li][item=171177] - A breadcrumb quest leading us to the Memories of Azeroth raid. From this quest line, we'll receive an item that can teleport us to Caverns of Time for the duration of the event.[/li]\n[/ul]\n\n[b]Video[/b]: https://youtu.be/kLSGFOoyJsA", "date": "2019-11-05T04:30:32-06:00", "rating": 7, "indent": 0, "roles": 256, "deleted": 0, "outofdate": 0, "userRating": 0, "replies": [], "dataTree": 1, "markupDisabledEnvironments": {"ptr": true, "beta": false}, "lastEdit": ["2019-11-05T08:43:01-06:00", 1, "Sipder2"]}
